    <item>
      <title>Get Serious With Virtual Real Estate Using Free Realms New Housing Directory</title>
      <link>http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/Free-realms-gamercom/~3/BXG1q1QEnRc/</link>
      <comments>http://www.free-realms-gamer.com/get-serious-with-virtual-real-estate-using-free-realms-new-housing-directory/#comments</comments>
      <pubDate>Mon, 17 Jan 2011 04:57:11 +0000</pubDate>
      <dc:creator>Free Realms Gamer</dc:creator>
      <category><![CDATA[Free Realms News]]></category>
      <category><![CDATA[Free Realms Tips]]></category>
      <category><![CDATA[Free Realms housing directory]]></category>
      <category><![CDATA[Free Realms updates]]></category>
      <category><![CDATA[house listings Free Realms]]></category>
      <category><![CDATA[SOE]]></category>
      <category><![CDATA[sony online entertainment]]></category>
      <guid isPermaLink="false">http://www.free-realms-gamer.com/?p=253</guid>
      <description>The good people at Sony Online Entertainment have upped the ante for property owners in the magical land of Free Realms by adding a searchable, user rated database of all registered homeowners.  Find out more... [...]&lt;br&gt;&lt;a type="audio/mpeg" href="http://podcasts.odiogo.com/get_mp3.mp3?f=/free-realms-gamer/Free_Realms_Gamer-Get_Serious_With_Virtual_Real_Estate_Using_Free_Realms_New_Housing_Directory.mp3"&gt;Click here to play&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;</description>
      <content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>Well, OK maybe not THAT serious.  But the good people at Sony Online Entertainment have upped the ante for property owners in the magical land of Free Realms by adding a searchable, user rated database of all registered homeowners.</p><p>With a few simple clicks you can either add your home to the directory, or search for the biggest, cushiest cribs in the land.</p><p>Here is what the Free Realms crew has to say about it:</p><blockquote><p>Once a house is in the directory other players can check it out without having to be on the friends list of the owner. Visitors can also vote on how cool a house is by giving it 1 to 5 stars.</p><p>You can search for a house by typing in the name of the owner or the house name. You can also see a list of the most popular homes currently on the list.</p><p>There are tabs for houses that belong to your friends and houses that have been recently added to the directory.</p><p>To visit a house, simply click the Visit! button!</p></blockquote><p><img src="http://www.free-realms-gamer.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/01/Free-Realms-house-search-filter-300x101.jpg?f65c71" alt="Free Realms house search filter" title="Free Realms house search filter" width="300" height="101" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-254" /></p><p>Although this isn&#8217;t so much a gameplay feature, it does help in discovering some pretty cool sights around the map you may not have had the chance to encounter, and what&#8217;s more it gives you a chance to meet new players who share similar tastes.  Now you can have a sweet backyard Robgoblin BBQ with the awesome neighbors you never even knew you had.</p><p>To access the Housing Directory just click on the icon that looks like a house from your toolbar or at the Welcome Screen.</p> 
<p><a href="http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~a/HcW70txo8igUOVi-7Y0J7t9gHjs/0/da"><img src="http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~a/HcW70txo8igUOVi-7Y0J7t9gHjs/0/di" border="0" ismap="true"></img></a><br/>
<a href="http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~a/HcW70txo8igUOVi-7Y0J7t9gHjs/1/da"><img src="http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~a/HcW70txo8igUOVi-7Y0J7t9gHjs/1/di" border="0" ismap="true"></img></a></p><div class="feedflare">
<a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/Free-realms-gamercom?a=BXG1q1QEnRc:UEuK1xYV8rk:yIl2AUoC8zA"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/Free-realms-gamercom?d=yIl2AUoC8zA" border="0"></img></a> <a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/Free-realms-gamercom?a=BXG1q1QEnRc:UEuK1xYV8rk:dnMXMwOfBR0"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/Free-realms-gamercom?d=dnMXMwOfBR0" border="0"></img></a> <a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/Free-realms-gamercom?a=BXG1q1QEnRc:UEuK1xYV8rk:F7zBnMyn0Lo"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/Free-realms-gamercom?i=BXG1q1QEnRc:UEuK1xYV8rk:F7zBnMyn0Lo" border="0"></img></a> <a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/Free-realms-gamercom?a=BXG1q1QEnRc:UEuK1xYV8rk:V_sGLiPBpWU"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/Free-realms-gamercom?i=BXG1q1QEnRc:UEuK1xYV8rk:V_sGLiPBpWU" border="0"></img></a> <a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/Free-realms-gamercom?a=BXG1q1QEnRc:UEuK1xYV8rk:qj6IDK7rITs"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/Free-realms-gamercom?d=qj6IDK7rITs" border="0"></img></a> <a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/Free-realms-gamercom?a=BXG1q1QEnRc:UEuK1xYV8rk:gIN9vFwOqvQ"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/Free-realms-gamercom?i=BXG1q1QEnRc:UEuK1xYV8rk:gIN9vFwOqvQ" border="0"></img></a> <a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/Free-realms-gamercom?a=BXG1q1QEnRc:UEuK1xYV8rk:TzevzKxY174"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/Free-realms-gamercom?d=TzevzKxY174" border="0"></img></a>
